{"type":"message","id":"f48f9c06","parentId":"086ee859","timestamp":"2026-03-09T07:29:25.367Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"浏览器又超时了。看来浏览器工具有问题。让我尝试用 exec 直接下载图片。我需要找到高渐离皮肤图片的直接 URL。\n\n根据王者荣耀的皮肤页面结构，皮肤图片通常在类似这样的 URL：\nhttps://game.gtimg.cn/images/yxzj/img201606/skin/hero-info/xxx/xxx-xxx.jpg\n\n高渐离的英雄 ID 是 138（根据记忆）。让我尝试下载这些图片。\n\n或者我可以用 web_search 搜索图片 URL。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_88aa8e0fef3e4ea0988e9ac6","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":10,"query":"site:game.gtimg.cn 高渐离 皮肤 海报 jpg"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773041350821}}
