{"type":"message","id":"a0dc4778","parentId":"85f49ad8","timestamp":"2026-03-09T07:30:38.870Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没有搜索结果。让我尝试直接访问王者荣耀的资源服务器下载高渐离皮肤图片。高渐离的英雄 ID 是 138。\n\n王者荣耀皮肤图片的 URL 格式通常是：\nhttps://game.gtimg.cn/images/yxzj/img201606/skin/hero-info/138/138-大皮肤 ID.jpg\n\n让我尝试用 exec 下载这些图片。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_87de64d9d10b4bb09ba2f4c7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /root/.openclaw/workspace/gaojianli_skins && cd /root/.openclaw/workspace/gaojianli_skins && curl -s -o default.jpg \"https://game.gtimg.cn/images/yxzj/img201606/skin/hero-info/138/138-0.jpg\" && curl -s -o siwang.jpg \"https://game.gtimg.cn/images/yxzj/img201606/skin/hero-info/138/138-1.jpg\" && curl -s -o wqu.jpg \"https://game.gtimg.cn/images/yxzj/img201606/skin/hero-info/138/138-13.jpg\" && curl -s -o tianxiu.jpg \"https://game.gtimg.cn/images/yxzj/img201606/skin/hero-info/138/138-11.jpg\" && curl -s -o luori.jpg \"https://game.gtimg.cn/images/yxzj/img201606/skin/hero-info/138/138-15.jpg\" && ls -la","timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773041366219}}
